ORG 100          / Start address of the program

LOAD H_ASCII    / Load ASCII value of 'H' into AC
OUTPUT          / Output the content of the AC
LOAD E_ASCII    / Load ASCII value of 'e' into AC
OUTPUT
LOAD L_ASCII    / Load ASCII value of 'l' into AC
OUTPUT
OUTPUT          / Output twice for two 'l' characters
LOAD O_ASCII    / Load ASCII value of 'o' into AC
OUTPUT

HALT             / Halt the program
H_ASCII, DEC 72  / ASCII value of 'H'
E_ASCII, DEC 101 / ASCII value of 'e'
L_ASCII, DEC 108 / ASCII value of 'l'
O_ASCII, DEC 111 / ASCII value of 'o'

END             / End of the program
